.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, collecting, filmmaking, hiking, video-games, woodworking
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, thriller, family, adventure, sports
 1. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
11. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
12. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person watching comedy movies##1
14. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
15. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
16. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |     3      |       4       |     5      |   6    |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | filmmaking | chess         | collecting | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure      | thriller      | family | disaster   | sports |

