.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-3::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, begonia, balloon-flower, aconite, lily
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, r&b, rock, soul, trance
 1. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
 3. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
 6. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
 7. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 8. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
 9. the fan of r&b is between the person who growslily and the fan of trance##2
10. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
11. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3    |    4     |    5    |    6     |
| Flower      | lily | poppy | aconite   | balloon-flower | daisy   | begonia |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | r&b         | trance | soul     | dubstep | rock     |

