 1. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 4. the person eating avocado is the person traveling to colone##1
 5. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
 7. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
10. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
11. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
13. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4    |       5       |    6     |
| City   | colone     | rome     | hamburg  | berlin     | prague | hannover |
| Food       | avocado | zucchini | garlic | apricot | pear          | radish   |

