.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-5::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, may, march, february, october, april
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, soccer
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
 4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
12. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |      4      |   5    |     6      |
| Birthday   | february | september     | april    | october | may | march    |
| Sport         | soccer  | basketball | badminton | cricket     | skiing | ice-hockey |

