.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-9::.
There 6 different types of food: cabbage, lettuce, strawberry, zucchini, pomegranate, watermelon
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile, subway, tram, van
 1. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
 2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 5. the person eating cabbage is the person eating cabbage##1
 6. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
 9. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
10. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating strawberry and the person driving the van##2
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
13. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
14. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person eating watermelon##5
15. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
16. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |    3     |     4      |    5    |   6    |
| Food   | zucchini | lettuce | pomegranate | strawberry     | watermelon | cabbage |
| Transport     | tram  | bike      | bus      | snowmobile | subway  | van    |

