.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-5-20::.
6 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, horse, lizard, snake
House: cottage, wooden, gothic-revival, futuristic, farmhouse, victorian
 1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the wooden house##1
 4. the owner of the fish is the farmhouse house##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the wooden house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
 8. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
 9. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
11. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Pet         | snake    | horse | fish   | hedgehog | ferret    | lizard |
| House   | cottage | victorian  | farmhouse | gothic-revival      | futuristic | wooden    |

 